title: Gucci Guccissima Large Emily Chain Bag
description: Gucci Guccissima large Emily chain bag in gold patent leather with GG pattern embossed. Featuring light gold-toned hardware, the signature 'Horsebit' embellishment that secures the front flap and the sliding chain link strap with leather pad in the centre. The flap opens to a cream textile interior with zip pocket and patched pockets. Approx dimensions: 36(Base-L) x 24cm (W) x 9cm (D), 26cm double chain drop. With Entrupy Certificate of Authenticity. (Pre-owned)
